(177, 1, '2021-04-12 19:48:48', '2021-04-12 19:48:48', '[et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" next_background_color=\"#ffffff\" admin_label=\"First section\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" background_image=\"http://localhost/psdwp/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/psd_02.png\" bottom_divider_style=\"slant\" bottom_divider_flip=\"horizontal\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"3_5,2_5\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"3_5\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_font=\"Montserrat|600|||||||\" text_text_color=\"#000000\"]<h1>Welcome to Houston Kidney Specialists Center</h1>\n<p>Houston Kidney Specialists Center is based in the Northwest Houston area. The practice is focused on caring for patients with kidney diseases including Acute Kidney Injury or Failure, Chronic Kidney Disease, Hemodialysis, Peritoneal Dialysis, HOME Dialysis, Post Kidney Transplantation Care , Cystic Kidney diseases, Glomerulonephritis , Diabetic kidney Diseases, Kidney Stones, Urine Abnormalities and Hypertension Management.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_5\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost/psdwp/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/dr_03.png\" alt=\"dr_03\" title_text=\"dr_03\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"About us setion\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\" top_divider_flip=\"horizontal\" bottom_divider_flip=\"horizontal\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"2_5,3_5\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"2_5\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost/psdwp/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/house_03.png\" alt=\"house_03\" title_text=\"house_03\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"3_5\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h1>Who we are? The Houstan Kidney Center Story</h1>\n<p>HKSC was founded on March 1st, 2019 by Dr. Devaraj Munikrishnappa and Dr. Ghayyath Sultan, after practicing in the same area for 10 years and 4 years respectively. They are experienced and passionate practicing Nephrologists, well trained in the field of Nephrology at St. Louis University, St. Louis, Missouri and University of Texas at San Antonio, Texas respectively. They are Board-Certified in Nephrology and are Diplomats of the American Board of Internal Medicine and Nephrology. They have over 14 years of experience in the field of Nephrology and over 35 years in the field of Medicine. Both have held physician leadership roles consistently. Dr. Munikrishnappa has been serving as Medical Director for Dialysis units. He has been invited to attend Physician Leadership Meetings</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" next_background_color=\"#ffffff\" admin_label=\"Portrait Section\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_image=\"http://localhost/psdwp/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/psd_02.png\" parallax=\"on\" bottom_divider_style=\"slant\" bottom_divider_flip=\"horizontal\" hover_enabled=\"0\" top_divider_style=\"slant\" top_divider_flip=\"vertical\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" prev_background_color=\"#ffffff\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_3,1_3,1_3\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_team_member name=\"Devaraj Munikrishnappa\" position=\"Managing Director\" image_url=\"http://localhost/psdwp/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/dr1_03.png\" _builder_version=\"4.9.3\" _module_preset=\"default\" body_fon